OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773227360
OL,3,CBAE system workers win above-inflation
OL,4,Cpay rise after months of strikes
OL,6,FThousands of workers at BAE Systems'
OL,7,FLancashire aerospace factories are
OL,8,Fcelebrating a major pay victory after
OL,9,Fmonths of strike action led to a
OL,10,Fsignificant above-inflation pay deal.
OL,12,FThe deal, secured by Unite the union,
OL,13,Fcovers staff at the Warton and
OL,14,FSamlesbury sites and includes a 6% pay
OL,15,Fincrease, extra annual leave, a one-
OL,16,Foff payment, and an earlier finish
OL,17,Ftime each day.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
