OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773227360
OL,3,CBAE system workers win above-inflation
OL,4,Cpay rise after months of strikes
OL,6,FThe breakthrough comes after staff
OL,7,Frepeatedly walked out in December,
OL,8,FJanuary, and February, protesting pay
OL,9,Foffers that lagged behind those given
OL,10,Fto colleagues elsewhere in the company.
OL,12,FDespite BAE's efforts to halt the
OL,13,Fstrikes through the High Court,
OL,14,Fworkers continued their industrial
OL,15,Faction until a deal was reached.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
