FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773227360
OL,3,CBAE system workers win above-inflation
OL,4,Cpay rise after months of strikes
OL,6,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,7,Fsaid: "It has taken a courageous
OL,8,Fstance from our workers on a picket
OL,9,Fline to win this award. They should be
OL,10,Fcongratulated for standing together
OL,11,Fand winning a pay rise they truly
OL,12,Fdeserve."
OL,14,FUnder the agreement, staff will
OL,15,Freceive a 4.8 per cent award backdated
OL,16,Fto 1 January and a further 0.75 per
OL,17,Fcent from 1 October 2026.
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@IO]
