PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773227360
OL,3,CBAE system workers win above-inflation
OL,4,Cpay rise after months of strikes
OL,6,FAll staff gain an extra day's annual
OL,7,Fleave, with Unite members receiving an
OL,8,Fadditional day, a one-off #500
OL,9,Fpayment, and a daily half-hour earlier
OL,10,Ffinish.
OL,12,FUnite regional officer Ross Quinn said
OL,13,F"This win shows the power in a union
OL,14,Fand that when our reps and workers
OL,15,Facross the aerospace industry and
OL,16,Facross Lancashire stand together, they
OL,17,Fcan win against even the biggest
OL,18,Femployers."
OL,26,@uD@AOUzD@KO]
